title: tutorial example code error.
body:
by **kevinwatt**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Open the tutorial document doc/go_tutorial.html

What is the expected output? What do you see instead?

At this tutorial page http://golang.org/doc/go_tutorial.html#tmp_17
The Example code is 

07    import fmt "fmt"  // Package implementing formatted I/O.

It'll course the syntax error, should be 

07    import "fmt"  // Package implementing formatted I/O.

Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)

4658:ac4d67277b86


Please provide any additional information below.
